OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FAs Iran grinds marine traffic through
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz to a halt, fears
OL,9,Frise over the effects on the global
OL,10,Feconomy, as large portions of the
OL,11,Fworld's oil and gas exports are
OL,12,Fpaused. ITV News Correspondent John
OL,13,FRay reports
OL,15,FA cargo vessel is on fire in the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz after being hit by an
OL,17,Funknown projectile, according to the
OL,18,FUK's maritime agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
