PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FUK Maritime Trade Operations (UKMTO)
OL,8,Fsaid: "The vessel has requested
OL,9,Fassistance and its crew are
OL,10,Fevacuating," the maritime authority
OL,11,Fsaid, adding that the ship was located
OL,12,Fabout 11 nautical miles north of
OL,13,FOman's Musandam Peninsula.
OL,15,F"Vessels are advised to transit with
OL,16,Fcaution and report any suspicious
OL,17,Factivity," said the UKMTO statement.
OL,19,FIran has not claimed the attack.
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@LO]wD@AOUyD@JO]
