OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FIsrael began what it said was an
OL,8,F"additional wave" of strikes on
OL,9,Ftargets in Tehran on Wednesday after
OL,10,FUS Secretary of Defence Pete Hegseth
OL,11,Fthreatened the US's "most intense day"
OL,12,Fof strikes on Iran.
OL,14,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Hegseth said the
OL,15,FUS would be deploying "the most
OL,16,Ffighters, the most bombers, the most
OL,17,Fstrikes" on Iran, as he vowed to
OL,18,Fpermanently end the country's ability
OL,19,Fto build a nuclear weapon.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]sD@UOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
