CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FIran continued to fire missiles and
OL,8,Fdrones at targets across the Gulf,
OL,9,Fincluding at oil infrastructure in
OL,10,FSaudi Arabia.
OL,12,FIran has effectively stopped tankers
OL,13,Ffrom using the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,14,Fshipping lane between the Persian Gulf
OL,15,Fand the Gulf of Oman ` the gateway to
OL,16,Fthe Indian Ocean ` through which 20%
OL,17,Fof the world's oil is carried.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
