OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FAttacks on merchant ships near the
OL,8,Fstrait have killed at least seven
OL,9,Fsailors, according to the
OL,10,FInternational Maritime Organisation.
OL,12,FThe US had said that on Tuesday, it
OL,13,Fdestroyed 16 mine-laying vessels as
OL,14,FIran threatens to block Gulf oil
OL,15,Fexports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
