OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FIran's allies, the Houthis in Yemen,
OL,8,Fare also threatening to close Bab el-
OL,9,FMandeb, a major trade route between
OL,10,FEurope and Asia, intelligence sources
OL,11,Ftold ITV News, which would have a near-
OL,12,Fimmediate impact on the availability
OL,13,Fand cost of imports like electronics
OL,14,Fand household goods.
OL,16,FThe strait, which lies between Yemen
OL,17,Fand Djibouti, also provides a route
OL,18,Ffor oil and liquefied natural gas to
OL,19,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
