PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FThe fire in the Strait of Hormuz comes
OL,8,Fafter sources claimed Iran has begun
OL,9,Flaying mines in the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,10,Fthe world's most important energy
OL,11,Fchokepoint that carries about one-
OL,12,Ffifth of all crude oil.
OL,14,FIran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,15,FCorps, which now effectively controls
OL,16,Fthe strait along with Iran's
OL,17,Ftraditional navy, has the capability
OL,18,Fto deploy a "gauntlet" of dispersed
OL,19,Fmine-laying craft, explosive-laden
OL,20,Fboats and shore-based missile
OL,21,Fbatteries, CNN has reported.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
