CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump said in a post
OL,8,Fon Truth Social on Tuesday that "if
OL,9,FIran has put out any mines in the
OL,10,FHormuz Strait, and we have no reports
OL,11,Fof them doing so, we want them
OL,12,Fremoved, IMMEDIATELY!"
OL,14,FHe added that "if for any reason mines
OL,15,Fwere placed, and they are not removed
OL,16,Fforthwith, the Military consequences
OL,17,Fto Iran will be at a level never seen
OL,18,Fbefore. If, on the other hand, they
OL,19,Fremove what may have been placed, it
OL,20,Fwill be a giant step in the right
OL,21,Fdirection!"
OL,26,@pD@aOUtD@VO]vD@OOU}D@KO]
