OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FIran under fire
OL,9,FThe Israel Defense Forces (IDF) said
OL,10,Fon Tuesday night that it had begun a
OL,11,Fnew "wave" of strikes on targets in
OL,12,FTehran.
OL,14,FIn a post on its Farsi page on X, the
OL,15,FIDF said: "The Israeli Defense Forces
OL,16,Fhave now launched a massive wave of
OL,17,Fattacks against the infrastructure of
OL,18,Fthe Iranian terrorist regime in
OL,19,FTehran."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
