OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FSix members of the Iranian women's
OL,8,Ffootball team were granted asylum
OL,9,Fafter calls for the Australian
OL,10,Fgovernment to help the women.
OL,12,FTrump joined Iranian groups urging the
OL,13,FAustralian government to help the
OL,14,Fwomen after they were knocked out of
OL,15,Fthe tournament over the weekend and
OL,16,Ffaced the prospect of returning to a
OL,17,Fcountry under bombardment and possible
OL,18,Fpunishment by the regime for not
OL,19,Fsinging the national anthem before
OL,20,Ftheir opening match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
