PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FHow did we get here?
OL,9,FIsrael and the US launched what they
OL,10,Fdescribed as "pre-emptive" strikes
OL,11,Fagainst Iran just before 6.30am on
OL,12,FFebruary 28, which they view as intent
OL,13,Fon acquiring nuclear weapons, shortly
OL,14,Fafter a round of negotiations.
OL,16,FIran denies seeking nuclear weapons,
OL,17,Fand some legal experts have said the
OL,18,Fattack violated international law. The
OL,19,FIslamic Republic has responded by
OL,20,Fstriking Israel and several targets in
OL,21,FGulf states allied with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
