PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773259871
OL,3,CShip on fire in Strait of Hormuz as
OL,4,CIsrael renews strikes on Iran and
OL,5,CLebanon
OL,7,FThe war's stated goals and timelines
OL,8,Fhave repeatedly shifted as the US has
OL,9,Fat times suggested it seeks to topple
OL,10,FIran's government or elevate new
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,FWhile US President Donald Trump
OL,14,Fpreviously dismissed the idea of boots
OL,15,Fon the ground in Iran, he did not rule
OL,16,Fit out when asked on Saturday.
OL,18,FHe said US troops could "possibly" be
OL,19,Fsent on the ground in Iran, as the war
OL,20,Fcontinues, but there would have to be
OL,21,Fa "very good reason".
